              <span
                style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#22c55e;font-weight:600;"
                >Live on Every Project</span
              >
            </div>
            <h3 class="heading-lg" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
              Your Personal <span class="gold-text"
                >Construction Dashboard</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="body-md" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
              From Day 1, every client receives a private link to their
              project's live dashboard — daily site photos, task checklists,
              concrete test results, structural drawings, and even <strong
                style="color:var(--text-primary);"
                >live CCTV access to your construction site</strong
              >. Watch your home being built — anytime, from anywhere. No more
              "what's happening at my site?"
            </p>
            <div
              style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:2rem;"
            >
              {
                [
                  {
                    icon: "📸",
                    label: "Daily Photo Log",
                    desc: "Site photos uploaded every evening — exact timestamp & stage",
                    highlight: false,
                  },
                  {
                    icon: "✅",
                    label: "Engineer Sign-offs",
                    desc: "Every steel, pour & plaster checked and digitally recorded",
                    highlight: false,
                  },
                  {
                    icon: "📐",
                    label: "Drawing Control Register",
                    desc: "All structural drawings, version-controlled and accessible",
                    highlight: false,
                  },
                  {
                    icon: "🧪",
                    label: "Curing & Cube Test Log",
                    desc: "M25 concrete strength records — 7-day and 28-day verified",
                    highlight: false,
                  },
                  {
                    icon: "📹",
                    label: "Live CCTV Access",
                    desc: "Watch your site live — 24/7 camera feed on your phone, anytime from anywhere",
                    highlight: true,
                  },
                ].map((f) => (
                  <div
